                                       KEYS (SHORTCUTS)
                                       ----------------


NUMERIC KEYPAD:

[ 1 ]     Decrease left engine
[ 3 ]     Decrease right engine
[ 2 ]     Decrease both engines

[ 4 ]     Start left engine
[ 6 ]     Start right engine

[ 5 ]     Activate Auto Pilot Hold Speed

[ 7 ]     Increase left engine
[ 8 ]     Increase both engines
[ 9 ]     Increase right engines

[ 0 ]     Turn on reverse throttle
[ . ]     Turn off reverse throttle

[ - ]     Stop left engine
[ Enter ] Stop right engine



CURSORKEYS:

[ Left ]  Increase preselected course
[ Right ] Decrease preselected course



KEYBOARD:

[ D ]     Enlarge cockpit view
[ S ]     Reduce cockpit view

[ E ]     Electronic Flight Control System [on/off]

[ J ]     Joystick [on/off]
[ N ]     Switch [day/night] -training only-
[ P ]     Pause [on/off]

[ Y ]            Increase preselected course NAV1
[ < / > ]        Decrease preselected course NAV1
