                                       LESSION IN FLYING
                                       -----------------

Sight-seeing flight at airport Koeln-Bonn.

Load program. when you've entered the office of the chief (ger. Büro
des Flugleiters) chose "training". Position the mousepointer on the word
"Training" at the bottom of the screen and press the left mouse button.

The Pilot-Logdiskette is not needed.


CREATING THE FLIGHT PLAN

- Create the appearing "Flight Plan" like this:

--------------------------------
         FLIGHT PLAN
--------------------------------

  [VFR]x   [IFR]           [ok]x


--------------------------------
FROM              [EDDK]
TO                [    ]
ETD               [1200]

--------------------------------
PAX               [55 ]  POB
FREIGHT           [24]  x 100Kg
FUEL              [30 ] x 100Kg
--------------------------------

After this we find ourselves at the start of the taxiway of airport
Koeln-Bonn.


With the key [J] the control can be switched from mouse to joystick and
back again. Make your decision just like you please.



