THE START (TAKE OFF)

Adjust the engine power with [8] - increase speed
and [2] - decrease speed  - all at the num. keypad.
Adjust so long as the Airbus rolls with  5-15 Knoten (speed)
at the runway. You can control the machine by moving
your joystick or mouse to the left and the right.
BE CAREFULL: The plane should be exactly in the middle of the
runway.
Press the SPACEBAR if you want to use the brakes. The course
(Heading) should be 140 degrees.


